The paper deals with image processing and vision, specifically image inpainting using patch-based texture synthesis. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The paper also involves optimization techniques and machine learning methods, which are relevant to the machine learning (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
